## Vim Plugins:
https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug

# Add to .vimrc:
  " Source plugins
    source ~/.vimrc.packages

# Install vim plugin manager, https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug
curl -fLo ~/.vim/autoload/plug.vim --create-dirs \
    https://raw.githubusercontent.com/junegunn/vim-plug/master/plug.vim

source ~/.vimrc.packages

# Install Plugin:
vim
# from vim run: :PlugInstall

## Add silversearcher-ag
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install -y automake pkg-config libpcre3-dev zlib1g-dev liblzma-dev

# < ubuntu 13
sudo apt-get install python-software-properties
sudo apt-get update

# go to: https://github.com/ggreer/the_silver_searcher and follow installation

## Add exuberant ctags
sudo apt-get install exuberant-ctags
  # to run from vim: :Tagbar


### Notes
:help [plugin_name]
